sentence: The following companies are expected to report earnings prior to market open on 05/17/2016.

Home Depot, Inc. ( HD ) is reporting for the quarter ending April 30, 2016.
The building company's consensus earnings per share forecast from the 11 analysts that follow the stock is $1.33.
This value represents a 14.66% increase compared to the same quarter last year.
In the past year HD has beat the expectations every quarter.
The highest one was in the 1st calendar quarter where they beat the consensus by 6.36%.

Zacks Investment Research reports that the 2017 Price to Earnings ratio for HD is 21.47 vs. an industry ratio of 17.20, implying that they will have a higher earnings growth than their competitors in the same industry.
